- [Bob] I saw a puppet show

00:00:05.925 --> 00:00:07.925
when I was six years old

00:00:08.823 --> 00:00:11.982
and I'm still talking about it.

00:00:11.982 --> 00:00:13.815
That was 80 years ago.

