00:02:05.610 --> 00:02:08.380
- [Bob] One of the things that I love,

00:02:08.380 --> 00:02:10.111
when I was performing,

00:02:10.111 --> 00:02:13.936
the little child will
look up at you and laugh.

00:02:13.936 --> 00:02:16.606
It's a wonderful sound.

00:02:16.606 --> 00:02:19.391
I wish I could go all
over the world doing that.

00:02:19.391 --> 00:02:22.558
