00:02:37.988 --> 00:02:39.110
- I don't think it's difficult

00:02:39.110 --> 00:02:40.884
to follow your passion.

00:02:40.884 --> 00:02:43.063
I do think it's easy to kind of lose sight

00:02:43.063 --> 00:02:45.212
of how much work is involved with that.

00:02:45.212 --> 00:02:47.919
The work involved with that is huge,

00:02:47.919 --> 00:02:49.457
it's giant.

00:02:49.457 --> 00:02:52.869
And it's very easy to get demoralized by

00:02:52.869 --> 00:02:54.161
things not working out

00:02:54.161 --> 00:02:57.364
because you're dealing with your passion.

00:02:57.364 --> 00:02:59.130
It kind of amplifies everything to 10

00:02:59.130 --> 00:03:02.269
to kind of being disappointed in things.

00:03:02.269 --> 00:03:04.347
You just need to kind of persevere.

00:03:04.347 --> 00:03:06.430
It's what you have to do.

00:03:17.112 --> 00:03:20.112
It's inspiring to me, everyday, that

00:03:21.225 --> 00:03:24.504
this place is filled
and bustling with people

00:03:24.504 --> 00:03:26.456
inspired by what Bob did.

00:03:26.456 --> 00:03:29.538
And, to this day, we
still say, Bob is with us.

00:03:29.538 --> 00:03:32.014
Bob's in all these lights,

00:03:32.014 --> 00:03:33.828
and these shows and these experiences

00:03:33.828 --> 00:03:36.654
and these things that kind of we put on.

00:03:36.654 --> 00:03:38.487
Bob has not passed on,

00:03:39.567 --> 00:03:42.650
his soul and heart is alive and well.

00:03:43.988 --> 00:03:45.655
That's what special.

